            "title" : "Matinée",
            "header" : "article-header-5b2d9e8bae86ed7f92ac88b1.jpg",
            "content_html" : "<h3 id=\"ambiance\">Ambiance:</h3>\n<p>We particularly liked the neon color furniture and industrial pipes, reminder of a fifty's US dinner. The place is large enough so you don't have to worry about finding a seat. Hold on to their <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/matineecoffee/\" target=\"_blank\">instagram</a> to have a good idea of what to expect.</p>\n<h3 id=\"cuisine\">Cuisine:</h3>\n<p>Matinée cuisine, is a mix of classic and less classic dishes. There aren't any real specialties like the <a href=\"article/5b2d9d5fae86ed7f92ac88a2\" target=\"_blank\">Shakshuka of Grandma's</a> but from their range you can always eat something you enjoy. The all day breakfast is the right place to find classic meal, like french toast and eggs on toast. Their lunch menu, starting at 11am will offer more diverse type of food like saffron pasta. Check their <a href=\"https://static1.squarespace.com/static/5a993e9b1137a65336bfe4e4/t/5aeae8ea575d1f6c1198c31c/1525344495371/matinee_menu_editable_14D.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">menu</a> to see more.</p>\n<h3 id=\"pricing\">Pricing:</h3>\n<p>All the menu is under $20 and you can get a full meal for $15. As for the coffee, a regular long black is $4. </p>\n<h3 id=\"service\">Service:</h3>\n<p>The place is generally quite, probably due to his recent opening. Which make the place perfect to enjoy a nice conversation while eating. The staff is welcoming and fast to take your order.</p>\n<h3 id=\"location\">Location:</h3>\n<p>The coffee shop is located only few hundred meters from Enmore Park, in a calm area of Marickville. The place is in itself quite easy to locate as it is on the main street. Check their <a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/Matinee+Coffee/@-33.9034834,151.1676001,15z/data=!4m5!3m4!1s0x0:0x2fb1c36ed10a957a!8m2!3d-33.9034834!4d151.1676001\" target=\"_blank\">address</a> to know precisely how to found them.</p>",
            "content_markdown" : "###Ambiance:\nWe particularly liked the neon color furniture and industrial pipes, reminder of a fifty's US dinner. The place is large enough so you don't have to worry about finding a seat. Hold on to their [instagram](https://www.instagram.com/matineecoffee/) to have a good idea of what to expect.\n\n###Cuisine:\nMatinée cuisine, is a mix of classic and less classic dishes. There aren't any real specialties like the [Shakshuka of Grandma's](article/5b2d9d5fae86ed7f92ac88a2) but from their range you can always eat something you enjoy. The all day breakfast is the right place to find classic meal, like french toast and eggs on toast. Their lunch menu, starting at 11am will offer more diverse type of food like saffron pasta. Check their [menu](https://static1.squarespace.com/static/5a993e9b1137a65336bfe4e4/t/5aeae8ea575d1f6c1198c31c/1525344495371/matinee_menu_editable_14D.pdf) to see more.\n\n###Pricing:\nAll the menu is under $20 and you can get a full meal for $15. As for the coffee, a regular long black is $4. \n\n###Service:\nThe place is generally quite, probably due to his recent opening. Which make the place perfect to enjoy a nice conversation while eating. The staff is welcoming and fast to take your order.\n\n###Location:\nThe coffee shop is located only few hundred meters from Enmore Park, in a calm area of Marickville. The place is in itself quite easy to locate as it is on the main street. Check their [address](https://www.google.com/maps/place/Matinee+Coffee/@-33.9034834,151.1676001,15z/data=!4m5!3m4!1s0x0:0x2fb1c36ed10a957a!8m2!3d-33.9034834!4d151.1676001) to know precisely how to found them.\n\n",
            "short_content" : "Arrived in 2018 in Marickville, Matinée is a nice place to have a brunch. It mixes diversity of food with its American diner style from the 50's.",
