            "title" : "White rabbit gallery",
            "content_html" : "<h3 id=\"ambiance\">Ambiance:</h3>\n<p>The Gallery, who use to be a Rolls-Royce service depot in the 40's has kept is warehouse style. The general ambiance really depend on the exhibition displayed at the time. The <a href=\"http://www.whiterabbitcollection.org/\" target=\"_blank\">white rabbit website</a> gives you some good insight on what you can expect of the gallery.</p>\n<h3 id=\"collection\">Collection:</h3>\n<p>Twice a year the gallery goes through a new lifting as a new collection is installed. That usually happens in February and August. Once there, and after visiting the 2 first floors, we recommend you to take the elevator as it is the only way to access the last floor of the exhibition. In this 3rd floor sits a massive art piece. Have a look to their <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/whiterabbitgallery/\" target=\"_blank\">instagram</a> to have a look of their artworks.</p>\n<h3 id=\"pricing\">Pricing:</h3>\n<p>The gallery entrance is completely <code>free</code>, as it is a non profit organization entirely funded by a philanthropist. A tea shop and a gift shop are also available.</p>\n<h3 id=\"location\">Location:</h3>\n<p>It is situated 10 minutes walk from central station, at the edge of the Central park mall complex. Check their <a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/30+Balfour+St,+Chippendale+NSW+2008/@-33.8865146,151.1980839,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x6b12ae278c5cb25d:0x196f4521266343a0!8m2!3d-33.8865146!4d151.2002726\" target=\"_blank\">address</a> to see how you can access it.</p>",
