            "content_html" : "<h3 id=\"ambiance\">Ambiance:</h3>\n<p>The cafe is incredibly warm. This is due to the <code>wooden walls and furniture in addition to the large walls of windows</code>. The building is new, but the  choice has been made to keep a industrial look with a partially finish roof. In addition to all of that, the place is extremely large, this is a good thing, because after leaving the <a href=\"article/5b2d9d6cae86ed7f92ac88a3\" target=\"_blank\">ground of Alexandria</a> just next door the last thing you want it to queue to be seated. The outdoor area deserve a special mention for its tropical style.</p>\n<h3 id=\"cuisine\">Cuisine:</h3>\n<h3 id=\"pricing\">Pricing:</h3>\n<p>We've been a bit surprise with the pricing, every meal cost $17. Witch is for us quite expensive for a lunch. For that price you had access to</p>\n<h3 id=\"service\">Service:</h3>\n<p>The service was really fast, we didn't had to wait very long to be seated neither to order. The waiters where also waiting for any sign of the customer, and happy to give information about the menu.</p>\n<h3 id=\"location\">Location:</h3>\n<p>The cafe is just a block away from the ground of Alexandria, and it is is main advantage to be honest. You can check its exact location <a href=\"https://www.google.com.au/maps/place/COOH+Alexandria/@-33.9106476,151.1932983,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x6b12b1b6d50648f9:0x2f8c1c2d941bd841!8m2!3d-33.9106521!4d151.195487\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.</p>",
